'''''The Person and the Challenges''''' is a biannual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] that was established in 2011. It is published by the [[Pontifical University of John Paul II]] in [[Kraków|Cracow]], Faculty of Theology, Section in [[Tarnów]]. The focus of the journal is the international exchange of ideas, evaluations, reports and studies on the person and contemporary challenges and the human dignity in the field of theology, education, canon law and social studies. The founder and current [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Józef Stala]]. Articles are in German, English, French, Italian and Spanish.<ref>The Faculty of Theology, Section in Tarnów, of the Pontifical University of John Paul II in Cracow. ''The Person and the Challenges.'' Volume 1 (2011) 1, {{ISSN|2083-8018}}</ref><ref>http://www.wt.diecezja.tarnow.pl/index.php/the-person-and-the-challenges/30-the-person-and-the-challenges/56-the-person-and-the-challenges-english</ref><ref>http://upjp2.edu.pl/strona/fsb85xjhhe</ref><ref>http://journals.indexcopernicus.com/passport.php?id=9364</ref><ref>http://www1.bg.us.edu.pl/bazy/czasopisma/czasop_full.asp?id=3752</ref><ref>http://ezb.uni-regensburg.de/?2693416</ref>
